NK040(thi)058:1: // sdig pa me yi mtha' gtad bzhugs so //
NK040(thi)058:3: gru gsum phung po me ri dgu klong nas //
NK040(thi)058:4: gnod byed 'dre gdon 'byung po'i gnyan po ni //
NK040(thi)058:5: khro bo'i sprul pa me yi sdig pa can //
NK040(thi)058:6: mgo dgu'i rwa ni bco brgyad nam mkha' gang //
NK040(thi)058:7: zhal dgu drag po 'brug sgra ti ri ri //
NK040(thi)058:8: ljag dgu glog zhag dmar po khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)058:9: rwa dgu'i rtsa la rdo rje thog mda' rgyug /
NK040(thi)058:10: mgo lus med par gnyer ma'i tsha tsha 'phros //
NK040(thi)058:11: gnyer ma'i nang nas zhal dang mche bas gang //
NK040(thi)058:12: ngar skad drag pos ri rab thal bar bsnyil //
NK040(thi)058:13: lus la me chen 'bar bas rgya mtsho skam //
NK040(thi)058:14: 'khros pa'i skan sgra nyi zla tshogs por 'phen //
NK040(thi)058:15: rngam pa'i stobs kyi stong gsum zhal du gsol //
NK040(thi)058:16: spyan gyi sdang mig lha srin 'dar zhing bsdangs //
NK040(thi)058:17: gnod byed gshed ma'i sdig pa nag po khyod //
NK040(thi)058:18: 'jigs byed me sdig dmar po zhal phyes shig /
NK040(thi)058:19: gnod byed nad gdon 'dul ba'i dus la bab //
NK040(thi)058:20: pho gdon 'byung po 'dul mo gdon srin mo 'dul
NK040(thi)058:21: klu gdon sa gdon 'dul gza' gdon rgyu skar gnod
NK040(thi)058:22: byed byad ma 'dul gri bo gshed 'khyams 'dul dmigs
NK040(thi)058:25: shar phyogs dur khrod me ri 'bar ba'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)058:26: me dpung mthing nag dgu klong dkyil 'khor nas //
NK040(thi)058:27: dri za pho mo bsnol ba'i gdan steng nas //
NK040(thi)058:28: jo mo lab sgron sku mdog mthing nag la //
NK040(thi)058:29: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK040(thi)058:30: mkha' 'gro'i cha lugs mche ba gtsigs //
NK040(thi)058:31: me yi ral pa lhabs se lhab //
NK040(thi)058:32: spyan gsum sdang mig kyi li li //
NK040(thi)058:33: zhal nas phata sgra lhangs se lhang //
NK040(thi)058:34: ljag la glog dmar khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)058:35: zhabs gnyis 'gying bag gar thabs kyi //
NK040(thi)058:36: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NK040(thi)058:37: sku la me yi tsha tsha 'phros //
NK040(thi)058:38: phyag g.yas me dpung 'bar ba bsnams //
NK040(thi)058:39: g.yon pas me yi hab zor brnams //
NK040(thi)058:41: nad gdon 'byung po thams cad bsregs //
NK040(thi)058:43: me dpung 'bar ba ci li li //
NK040(thi)058:44: me yi zhags pa khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)058:45: me yi tsha tsha dpungs se dpung //
NK040(thi)058:46: me yi se ba tha ra ra //
NK040(thi)058:47: me yi char pa si li li //
NK040(thi)058:48: me yi mkha' 'gro thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)058:49: me yi thog mda' sha ra ra //
NK040(thi)058:50: me yi 'ur sgra ti ri ri //
NK040(thi)058:51: me yi 'khor lo ci li li //
NK040(thi)058:53: lus dang lus gdon bcas pa dang //
NK040(thi)058:54: bar chad 'dre gdon pho mo rnams //
NK040(thi)058:55: me dpung 'bar ba'i gzhob tu bsreg /
NK040(thi)058:56: ram ram pho gdon 'byung po ram //
NK040(thi)058:57: ram ram mo gdon srin mo ram //
NK040(thi)058:58: ram ram gdon bgegs thams cad ram //
NK040(thi)058:59: ram ram nad 'dre dri bo ram //
NK040(thi)058:60: ram ram bar chad rkyen rnams ram //
NK040(thi)058:61: dmigs pa bsgrims la phata dgu bya /
NK040(thi)058:63: lho phyogs dur khrod me ri dgu //
NK040(thi)058:64: me dpung ser nag gshin rje pho mo jo mo lab sgron sku mdog ser nag la //
NK040(thi)058:67: nub phyogs dur khrod me ri me dpung dmar nag
NK040(thi)058:68: klu gdon jo mo lab sgron sku mdog dmar nag
NK040(thi)058:70: byang phyogs dur khrod me ri me dpung ljang nag
NK040(thi)058:71: gnod sbyin jo mo lab sgron sku mdog ljang nag
NK040(thi)058:73: dbus phyogs me dpung smug nag gza' gdon pho mo jo mo lab sgron sku mdog smug nag la //
NK040(thi)058:75: 'og phyogs dur khrod me dpung smug nag sa bdag
NK040(thi)058:76: pho mo jo mo lab sgron sku mdog nag po
NK040(thi)058:78: mtshams bzhi dur khrod me dpung sna tshogs me lha'i pho mo rlung lha'i gdan steng nas //
NK040(thi)058:79: jo mo lab sgron sku mdog sna tshogs la //
NK040(thi)058:80: zhal gcig yul nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i me ri dgu klong 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK040(thi)058:81: bdud bzhi pho mo bsnol ba'i yi dam rgyal ba'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)058:82: zhal gcig yi dam lha tshogs 'bum gyis bskor //
NK040(thi)058:83: yi dam lha tshogs thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)058:85: byang phyogs bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod nas //
NK040(thi)058:86: me dpung rlung nag dgu klong nad gdon dgra bgegs bsnol ba'i chos skyong ma mgon lcam dral rnams //
NK040(thi)058:87: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK040(thi)058:88: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK040(thi)058:89: chos skyong pho ma'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK040(thi)058:90: me yi ral pa lhabs se lhab //
NK040(thi)058:91: spyan gsum sdang mig kyi li li //
NK040(thi)058:92: zhal nas phata sgra lhangs se lhang //
NK040(thi)058:93: ljags la glog dmar khyugs se khyug /
NK040(thi)058:94: zhabs gnyis 'gying bag gar thabs kyi //
NK040(thi)058:95: me dpung 'bar ba'i nang la bzhugs //
NK040(thi)058:96: sku la phyag g.yon me nad gdon chos skyong pho rgyud mo brgyud rnams //
NK040(thi)058:97: me yi me yi tsha tsha dpungs se me yi ser ba tha ra ra //
NK040(thi)058:98: me yi char pa si li li //
NK040(thi)058:99: me yi mkha' 'gro thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)058:100: me yi thog mda' sha ra ra //
NK040(thi)058:101: me yi 'ur sgra ti ri ri //
NK040(thi)058:102: me yi 'khor lo ci li li //
NK040(thi)058:104: lus dang lus gdon bcas pa dang //
NK040(thi)058:105: bar chad 'dre gdon pho mo rnams //
NK040(thi)058:106: me dpung 'bar ba'i ram ram pho gdon ram ram mo gdon ram ram nad 'dre gdon bgegs ram /
NK040(thi)058:109: phrin las nad gdon tshar gcod do //
NK040(thi)058:111: zhugs ma'i zhags pas thun brdeg na //
NK040(thi)058:112: sbang ma rkam po barngosa se btags //
NK040(thi)058:113: de la mar nag khu bas sbags //
NK040(thi)058:114: de nyid zhugs mer brgyab pa'i dus //
NK040(thi)058:115: phyar ba tsam gyis me chad nges //
NK040(thi)058:116: yang na lci ba ser ka ma'i //
NK040(thi)058:117: phye ma byas kyang rung tsam yin //
NK040(thi)058:118: mkhar gong phye zhib dang bsres na //
NK040(thi)058:119: me lce rgyang ring chad pa yin //
NK040(thi)058:120: yang na ra tshil zhun phye sbyar //
NK040(thi)058:122: yang na mar nag btsan dug phye //
NK040(thi)058:123: chang la bul tog btab pa byug /
NK040(thi)058:124: sla ngar bskor ba bskam pa'i phyes //
NK040(thi)058:125: sgra bcas mes khyim gang bar mched //
NK040(thi)058:126: de yi sngon du byang bul chus //
NK040(thi)058:127: khyim kun byug pas mi tshig go //
NK040(thi)058:128: 'dre gdon brab sogs drag las kyi //
NK040(thi)058:129: me hom sbar la nyer mkho 'di //
NK040(thi)058:130: sa man+ta yi sug bris spel //
